We won't be able to come to restaurants either.

870
00:57:32,970 --> 00:57:35,010
I'll really treat you well.

871
00:57:39,190 --> 00:57:40,100
Is that all?

872
00:57:41,690 --> 00:57:44,480
Is there anything else you need?

873
00:57:47,400 --> 00:57:49,030
Say you'll tear out your heart for me.

874
00:57:50,030 --> 00:57:51,820
Yeah, I'll tear out my heart for you.

875
00:58:25,270 --> 00:58:27,190
-Pretty good, right?
-That was great.

876
00:58:27,190 --> 00:58:28,030
Right?

877
00:58:32,610 --> 00:58:34,030
So cute.

878
00:58:37,330 --> 00:58:38,370
Look over here.

879
00:58:41,330 --> 00:58:45,040
Are you the owner of 0486?

880
00:58:45,840 --> 00:58:46,920
Yeah, that's me.

881
00:58:46,920 --> 00:58:50,010
Could you move your Mercedes?

882
00:58:50,090 --> 00:58:51,130
Sorry.

883
00:58:53,970 --> 00:58:55,890
I'm gonna live in a house like this later.

884
00:58:55,890 --> 00:58:56,640
Yeah.

885
