There's something inside.

886
00:58:59,270 --> 00:59:00,350
Look.

887
00:59:00,350 --> 00:59:01,140
Where?

888
00:59:03,350 --> 00:59:04,940
There's more, there's more.

889
00:59:06,270 --> 00:59:07,730
Oh, you curl your hair like this.

890
00:59:07,730 --> 00:59:09,280
Yeah, curl it up.

891
00:59:10,570 --> 00:59:11,570
Exactly.

892
00:59:11,780 --> 00:59:13,030
Can I curl it hard?

893
00:59:13,030 --> 00:59:13,910
Yeah.

894
00:59:14,700 --> 00:59:17,780
-Feels good.
-I'm busy.

895
00:59:17,950 --> 00:59:20,620
-Okay, see you later.
-Nice.

896
00:59:24,420 --> 00:59:26,920
Lucky Dream

897
00:59:25,040 --> 00:59:27,540
-Is it good?
-What's it about?

898
00:59:33,550 --> 00:59:35,260
We won, we won!

899
00:59:37,760 --> 00:59:38,930
We won!

900
00:59:38,930 --> 00:59:41,680
It's the key part of the tally book.

901
00:59:41,680 --> 00:59:42,980
-Don't sleep.
-Yep.

902
01:00:02,250 --> 01:00:04,790
Help yourself if you need it

903
01:00:08,130 --> 01:00:08,920
You tired?

904
01:00:11,630 --> 01:00:12,210
Jeong-won.

905
01:00:12,210 --> 01:00:12,800
Yeah?

906
01:00:12,800 --> 01:00:13,840
You sure you're actually pushing?

907
01:00:15,090 --> 01:00:16,510
Hey, Eun-ho. Let's jump together.

908
01:00:16,680 --> 01:00:17,390
I can't get up.

909
01:00:17,720 --> 01:00:18,470
Come on!

910
01:00:18,470 --> 01:00:19,640
Get up!

911
01:00:20,510 --> 01:00:20,850
Some encouragement?

912
01:00:21,390 --> 01:00:21,720
What?

913
01:00:21,720 --> 01:00:22,270
Some encouragement.

914
01:00:27,230 --> 01:00:28,190
Okay, I'm getting up.

915
01:00:28,610 --> 01:00:29,610
I'm fine now!

916
01:00:29,730 --> 01:00:30,690
Totally fine!

917
01:00:35,190 --> 01:00:35,900
Hot, right?

918
01:00:37,110 --> 01:00:37,950
Should we get an air conditioner?

919
01:00:38,490 --> 01:00:40,910
Buy a new one? Maybe five of them?

920
01:00:41,580 --> 01:00:42,290
Stop it.

921
01:00:42,660 --> 01:00:44,290
You know that house
I'm building in Hannam-dong?

922
01:00:44,370 --> 01:00:45,660
Once it's done, we'll move in there.

923
01:00:46,160 --> 01:00:46,660
Okay.

924
01:00:47,120 --> 01:00:47,870
And while we're at it,

925
01:00:48,790 --> 01:00:50,340
let's have some kids. Like, three.

926
01:00:50,750 --> 01:00:51,340
No way.

927
01:00:51,670 --> 01:00:52,050
Why?

928
01:00:52,840 --> 01:00:55,050
If we're both working, we'll be too busy.

929
01:00:59,140 --> 01:01:00,220
How about you

930
01:01:01,350 --> 01:01:02,430
prep for TOEIC after
taking a break from school?

931
01:01:04,430 --> 01:01:05,180
For architecture,

932
01:01:06,350 --> 01:01:08,390
you need to pass the architect exam.

933
01:01:09,770 --> 01:01:11,060
Let's start now.

934
01:01:11,770 --> 01:01:13,070
You can do it.

935
01:01:16,530 --> 01:01:18,030
I'm not earning enough
to cover my tutoring costs.

936
01:01:18,700 --> 01:01:20,240
I'll invest in you.

937
01:01:20,240 --> 01:01:21,410
I'll support you.

938
01:01:22,120 --> 01:01:23,950
But in return, you'll build me a huge house

939
01:01:24,290 --> 01:01:26,410
with a garden,

940
01:01:26,410 --> 01:01:27,960
and you standing in it.

941
01:01:29,500 --> 01:01:30,120
Deal?

942
01:01:30,580 --> 01:01:30,960
Yeah.

943
01:01:38,090 --> 01:01:38,760
Great.

944
01:01:40,800 --> 01:01:41,510
Eun-ho.

945
01:01:41,680 --> 01:01:42,100
Yeah?

946
01:01:42,970 --> 01:01:44,970
Even if we break up someday,
let's see each other sometimes.

947
01:01:48,020 --> 01:01:48,940
I'm not breaking up with you.

948
01:01:53,110 --> 01:01:53,690
Come here.

949
01:01:55,110 --> 01:01:55,730
Let's just live like this.

950
01:01:57,070 --> 01:01:59,570
It's so outdated, why are you
making a game like this?

951
