Stuff like this doesn't sell these days.

953
01:02:08,290 --> 01:02:09,540
Lee Eun-ho!

954
01:02:14,420 --> 01:02:16,090
You don't seem to
have gained much weight.

955
01:02:16,460 --> 01:02:17,260
Why are you so light?

956
01:02:17,260 --> 01:02:18,420
I have gained some.

957
01:02:18,760 --> 01:02:19,630
-Really? -Yeah.

958
01:02:19,800 --> 01:02:20,380
Then let's take a taxi.

959
01:02:21,680 --> 01:02:23,470
Are you crazy? Let's just take the bus.

960
01:02:24,100 --> 01:02:25,050
No, we can take a taxi.

961
