Why?

962
01:02:27,010 --> 01:02:28,560
What did they say
about your game? Good?

963
01:02:28,770 --> 01:02:29,600
They said it was really good.

964
01:02:30,600 --> 01:02:31,980
So I changed my plans.

965
01:02:33,100 --> 01:02:35,310
Had meetings at a few places,
need to pick one.

966
01:02:39,360 --> 01:02:41,990
It'll work out, don't worry.

967
01:02:43,070 --> 01:02:43,660
Of course.

968
01:02:45,580 --> 01:02:46,330
Let's take a taxi.

969
01:02:48,200 --> 01:02:50,250
Taxi!

970
01:02:52,670 --> 01:02:54,750
Taxi!

971
01:03:06,600 --> 01:03:07,680
So black.

972
01:03:20,030 --> 01:03:21,990
With a disease this severe,
you probably can't see clearly.

973
01:03:22,490 --> 01:03:23,820
You mentioned you have diabetes too.

974
01:03:24,490 --> 01:03:27,330
Cataracts can be delayed, but not be cured.

975
01:03:27,330 --> 01:03:29,580
There's a chance it could
eventually lead to blindness.

976
01:03:30,290 --> 01:03:32,330
Let's run some detailed tests first.

977
