Hey, Jeong-won! Hey!

978
01:03:39,590 --> 01:03:40,250
What?

979
01:03:40,510 --> 01:03:43,970
Can you really balance work and exam prep?

980
01:03:44,880 --> 01:03:47,430
The exam is held annually.
I'll just try again next year.

981
01:03:47,640 --> 01:03:50,060
Think of it as me working
and studying at the same time.

982
01:03:50,770 --> 01:03:52,270
About my dad,

983
01:03:53,390 --> 01:03:54,230
I'll handle it myself.

984
01:03:54,810 --> 01:03:56,150
Stop talking about it like
it's someone else's problem, okay?

985
01:03:57,100 --> 01:04:00,070
If you broke your leg, would you
tell me to handle it myself too?

986
01:04:00,070 --> 01:04:01,650
That's different.

987
01:04:01,650 --> 01:04:03,320
-How can you say that...
-It's the same.

988
01:04:05,240 --> 01:04:06,700
Once I find a job,

989
01:04:07,030 --> 01:04:08,320
I can get a loan,

990
01:04:08,320 --> 01:04:09,160
and you can keep studying.

991
01:04:09,530 --> 01:04:11,450
I don't want you to give up on your game.

992
01:04:11,450 --> 01:04:13,080
I want to help you too.

993
01:04:13,910 --> 01:04:15,500
Oh my god, what should we do?

994
01:04:15,870 --> 01:04:17,670
Yeah, seriously, what should we do?

995
01:04:26,010 --> 01:04:26,380
Are you crying?

996
