1417
01:42:29,000 --> 01:42:30,290
And I received it all.

1418
01:42:33,670 --> 01:42:36,090
Eun-ho, I want to tell you something.

1419
01:42:39,050 --> 01:42:40,220
Thank you for

1420
01:42:43,890 --> 01:42:46,770
