To Jeong-won

1431
01:45:54,870 --> 01:45:55,910
Jeong-won.

1432
01:45:58,580 --> 01:46:02,500
Jeong-won. How are you doing?

1433
01:45:59,170 --> 01:46:00,460
How are you doing?

1434
