Calling Jeong-won

1438
01:46:17,350 --> 01:46:21,900
I heard from Eun-ho recently
that you two broke up.

1439
01:46:24,440 --> 01:46:26,990
I was always grateful
you ate them with such joy,

1440
01:46:28,200 --> 01:46:29,950
