1441
01:46:35,620 --> 01:46:39,250
Fate is a strange thing. It would be wonderful
if you two could stay together forever.

1442
01:46:39,920 --> 01:46:43,790
But it's not easy to avoid
disappointing each other.

1443
01:46:39,960 --> 01:46:43,000
Eun-ho's Table

1444
01:46:45,880 --> 01:46:48,510
Eun-ho's Table
In mourning

1445
01:46:46,300 --> 01:46:49,880
After all, hearts change,
and life changes. It's inevitable.

1446
01:46:54,140 --> 01:46:55,640
But that's okay.

1447
01:46:57,890 --> 01:46:59,060
It's okay.

1448
01:47:13,490 --> 01:47:16,870
I don't know if this letter will reach you,

1449
01:47:13,950 --> 01:47:20,250
To Jeong-won

1450
01:47:17,990 --> 01:47:19,910
